CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, pg. 3 reads: "Cute 'Honeybunnies' Paraded... and captured the hears of everyone at the fashion show at A. Leo Weil School. Wearing perky spring outfits with sparkling smiles on their faces, some came out in pairs, as a single, or in one instance, as a trio.  Left to right:...William Ferguson.. "
TitMainTitle: Portrait of William Ferguson modeling suit, light colored overcoat, and fedora, standing on stage in A. Leo Weil School for Easter fashion show
